CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

August 13, 2008

[Cite as 08/13/2008 Case Announcements #2, 2008-0hio-4072.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2008-0395. Disciplinary Counsel v. Freeman.

This matter is pending before the court upon the report of the Board of Commissioners on Grievances and Discipline. On May 12, 2008, respondent filed a request to seal mitigating factors contained in the board’s report. Upon consideration thereof,

It is ordered by the court that the request to seal is denied.
